  "detailed_description": "<strong>You Are Tre</strong> is about tree in a beautiful environment. Experience endless tree life, growing and witnessing the nature itself.<br>And all it's glory and power with <strong>dynamic cinematic-quality weather effects</strong>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404610/extras/0915fede48bb62f1cc33f16c1baf5865.poster.avif?t=1692104236\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404610/extras/0915fede48bb62f1cc33f16c1baf5865.webm?t=1692104236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404610/extras/0915fede48bb62f1cc33f16c1baf5865.mp4?t=1692104236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Real time changing <strong>day/night cycle</strong> (same time as in your location!)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404610/extras/6f9aef005340fe7366789a492f414497.poster.avif?t=1692104236\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404610/extras/6f9aef005340fe7366789a492f414497.webm?t=1692104236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404610/extras/6f9aef005340fe7366789a492f414497.mp4?t=1692104236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>And a lot of random events like animals, airplanes, and maybe even something mystical.. Don't miss it! <br><br>Features:<br>- Real life time speed<br>- Seasons<br>- Different weather conditions<br>- Real time growth<br>- Different trees to choose<br>- Random events<br>- And more..",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>You Are Tre</strong> is about tree in a beautiful environment. Experience endless tree life, growing and witnessing the nature itself.<br>And all it's glory and power with <strong>dynamic cinematic-quality weather effects</strong>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404610/extras/0915fede48bb62f1cc33f16c1baf5865.poster.avif?t=1692104236\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404610/extras/0915fede48bb62f1cc33f16c1baf5865.webm?t=1692104236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404610/extras/0915fede48bb62f1cc33f16c1baf5865.mp4?t=1692104236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Real time changing <strong>day/night cycle</strong> (same time as in your location!)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404610/extras/6f9aef005340fe7366789a492f414497.poster.avif?t=1692104236\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404610/extras/6f9aef005340fe7366789a492f414497.webm?t=1692104236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404610/extras/6f9aef005340fe7366789a492f414497.mp4?t=1692104236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>And a lot of random events like animals, airplanes, and maybe even something mystical.. Don't miss it! <br><br>Features:<br>- Real life time speed<br>- Seasons<br>- Different weather conditions<br>- Real time growth<br>- Different trees to choose<br>- Random events<br>- And more..",
